TextEng: Yes! I challenge fate daily to prove myself worthy.
Text: 그래요! 매일 운명에 도전해서 제 가치를 증명하죠.

TextEng: Uh... sure. I guess you like to fight?
Actually, I think I would rather live in a nice, peaceful age.
Text: 사실, 평화로운 시대에 사는 게 더 좋겠어요.

TextEng: Yes! Me love to fight!
Um... okay, if you say. You like fights?
Text: 음... 알았어, 네가 그러면. 싸움 좋아해?

TextEng: No. Me like peace. Me no like fights.
Text: 아니. 나 평화 좋아. 나 싸움 싫어.

TextEng: No. There is a time for fighting and a time for talking, but a wise person knows the difference.
Text: 아니요. 싸울 때가 있고 대화할 때가 있는데, 현명한 사람은 그 차이를 알죠.

TextEng: There is very little that one cannot accomplish using the mind instead of the body.
Text: 몸 대신 머리를 쓰면 못할 일이 거의 없어요.

TextEng: It's small-minded people like you who cause war and destruction in the world.
Text: 당신 같은 속 좁은 사람들이 세상에 전쟁과 파괴를 일으키는 거예요.

TextEng: You keep getting in my face and I'll show you how the strong survive!
Text: 계속 시비 걸면 강한 자가 어떻게 살아남는지 보여줄게!

TextEng: No. There be time for fight and time for talk. Me like both.
Text: 아니. 싸울 때 있고 말할 때 있어. 나 둘 다 좋아.

TextEng: Me like to be sneaky instead. Get stuff done better that way.
Text: 나 몰래 하는 거 좋아. 그게 더 잘 돼.

TextEng: You watch mouth or me knock you on that skinny butt!
Text: 입 조심해 안 그러면 그 마른 엉덩이 때려줄 거야!

TextEng: You folks cause war and death. Me not like you.
Text: 너네가 전쟁이랑 죽음 만들어. 나 너네 싫어.

TextEng: What's been going on around here?
Nothing. Goodbye.
What going on here?
What do you do here?
What your job be?
Can I challenge one of the druids?
Text: 드루이드 중 한 명에게 도전할 수 있나요?

TextEng: All right. Goodbye.
Yes.
No.
I am ready for the challenge.
Yes.
No. I have some questions first.
No. Me want ask question first.
Could you explain the rules again?
Text: 규칙을 다시 설명해 주실 수 있나요?

TextEng: Could you tell me more about the person I am fighting?
Text: 제가 싸울 상대에 대해 더 알려주시겠어요?

TextEng: I'm not ready for a fight yet.
What be rules again?
Me want know more 'bout person me fighting.
Text: 나 싸울 놈 더 알고 싶어.

TextEng: Me not ready for fight yet.
Text: 나 아직 싸울 준비 안 됐어.

TextEng: Nevermind. I am ready to fight now.
Okay. Me ready for fight.
I will go talk to him then. Goodbye.
Text: 그럼 그 사람한테 가서 말해볼게요. 안녕히.

TextEng: Me go talk to him. Bye bye.
Text: 나 걔한테 말하러 가. 잘 가.

TextEng: Me want fight druid.
Tell me why you are here again.
I be ready for challenge.
Why you be here again?
Yes.
Not yet.
Yes.
Not yet.

No.
Yes.
No.
Goodbye.
No.
